eg:   ALTER TABLE Students
      ADD COLUMN Roll No INT;
          - It adds a new column in the table 


eg:   ALTER TABLE Students
      MODIFY COLUMN Roll No SMALLINT;
          -It changes its value from int into smallint

eg:   ALTER TABLE Students
      CHANGE COLUMN Roll No Roll_No;
          - It renames Roll No into Roll_No

eg:   ALTER TABLE student
      DROP COLUMN email;
           - It drops/remove column called email from the table



